-- Libyan Central Bank Establishes Commission to Check Corruption
-- B y   E d i t o r s :   [ b n : P R S N = 1 5 1 1 8 1 2 0 ]   L o u i s   M e i x l e r   [ ]
-- 2012-06-24T11:09:50Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-24/libyan-central-bank-establishes-commission-to-check-corruption.html
The Central Bank of Libya has set
up a commission to investigate corruption in the banking
industry during the rule of former leader  Muammar Qaddafi .  Central bank Governor Saddek Omar Elkaber appointed the
seven-member group and said it will evaluate and act on
complaints, according to a statement from the bank. 